    description:
      'Türkiye\'nin lider levha üreticisinin Ana Bayisi olarak tüm portföyü stoktan sunuyoruz. Türkiye genelinde sevkiyat imkânı.',
    icon: `<rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1" stroke-width="1.5" /><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1" stroke-width="1.5" /><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1" stroke-width="1.5" /><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1" stroke-width="1.5" />`,
    href: '/urunler/kastamonu-entegre',
